   <title>
    地政總署署長：現時對違規雜物執管工作非最有效
   </title>
   <link>
    https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E6%94%BF%E7%B6%93/%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%BF%E7%B8%BD%E7%BD%B2%E7%BD%B2%E9%95%B7%EF%BC%9A%E7%8F%BE%E6%99%82%E5%B0%8D%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E9%9B%9C%E7%89%A9%E5%9F%B7%E7%AE%A1%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E9%9D%9E%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88
