<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/26365UP6d3" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53704565593_c07706c612_c.jpg" width="800" alt="無標題" /></a><br /><em>黎志華、身兼民政專員的區議會主席黃昕然</em></p>
<p>被問到閒置政府土地，黎志華指全港<a href="https://www.landsd.gov.hk/tc/land-mgt-enforce/short-term-tenancy.html">有200幅空置土地及校舍可供申請</a>，其中7幅位於深水埗區，有興趣的市民或機構可到地政總署網站查看。身兼港超聯球隊晉峰會長的黃俊雄，問及<a href="//efaidnbmnnnibpcajpcglclefindmkaj/https://www.wsd.gov.hk/filemanager/en/content_1354/12_R2022_020_Sham%20Shui%20Po_d.pdf">水庫</a>頂能否興建康樂設施，黎志華稱視乎個別情況。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/89LDh8o093" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53704348146_7f16c409b4_c.jpg" width="800" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
